data.description:
***SELLER IS OFFERING A $15,000 BUYER'S CREDIT TO USE TOWARDS LENDER RATE BUY DOWN OR DEDUCT FROM $725K OFFER PRICE***

Welcome home to 10222 Cavaletti Drive!!  This beautiful Chatfield Farms two story property has been well maintained by the original owners.  The main floor has high vaulted ceilings with an abundance of windows, making the home feel bright and spacious. The newly updated kitchen is open to the family room and nearby trex deck offering ease of entertainment with friends or just the ability to spread out as a family and still be close. The upstairs boasts the primary suite along with two additional bedrooms with a shared full bath.  The lower level has been partially finished with a bedroom and 3/4 bath, offering privacy for your teenager or overnight guests. This Roxborough gem is perfectly located for the family that enjoys the outdoors.  Chatfield State Park, Roxborough State Park and Waterton Canyon are all minutes from the home.  You can bike on the neighborhood trails that lead to the Highline Canal, hike or fish.  Something for everyone!  You don't want to miss out on this one.  Come take a look!
